{"article_id":"y8GtOVTlcZy0fckj","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Washington ( CNN )","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"Former acting FBI Director Andrew McCabe says","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"Deputy Attorney General Rod Rosenstein raised high-level discussions at the Justice Department","depth":10},{"id":3,"text":"about recruiting Cabinet members","depth":11},{"id":4,"text":"to invoke the 25th Amendment","depth":12},{"id":5,"text":"to remove President Donald Trump from office in the aftermath of former FBI Director James Comey 's firing .","depth":12},{"id":6,"text":"The discussions also included speculation","depth":11},{"id":7,"text":"about which Cabinet members could be on board with the idea ,","depth":11},{"id":8,"text":"McCabe said in an interview with CBS 's Scott Pelley .","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"Rosenstein , through a Justice Department spokesperson , has repeatedly disputed McCabe 's characterization of his remarks ,","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"though he has not denied","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"the topic was discussed at some point .","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"McCabe ,","depth":12},{"id":13,"text":"who was fired from the FBI last March ,","depth":12},{"id":14,"text":"also told CBS","depth":11},{"id":15,"text":"he ordered an investigation","depth":11},{"id":16,"text":"into whether Trump obstructed justice as a way","depth":13},{"id":17,"text":"to preserve ongoing inquiries into Russian election meddling","depth":13},{"id":18,"text":"in case there was an effort","depth":13},{"id":19,"text":"to terminate them .","depth":13},{"id":20,"text":"The comments resurface the extraordinary tension between Trump and the nation 's top law enforcement officials ,","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"though a number of the ones","depth":12},{"id":22,"text":"who worked with McCabe in the early days of the administration","depth":12},{"id":23,"text":"have since been dismissed or resigned .","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"Rosenstein `` raised the issue","depth":13},{"id":25,"text":"( of the 25th Amendment )","depth":13},{"id":26,"text":"and discussed it with me in the context","depth":13},{"id":27,"text":"of thinking about how many other Cabinet officials might support such an effort , ''","depth":13},{"id":28,"text":"McCabe said in a transcript","depth":12},{"id":29,"text":"released by CBS on Friday .","depth":12},{"id":30,"text":"He added","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"that Rosenstein was `` counting votes or possible votes '' of different Cabinet members","depth":12},{"id":32,"text":"who","depth":14},{"id":33,"text":"he thought","depth":14},{"id":34,"text":"would support removing the President .","depth":13},{"id":35,"text":"When Pelley asked","depth":12},{"id":36,"text":"if Rosenstein seemed focused on getting rid of Trump ,","depth":12},{"id":37,"text":"McCabe said","depth":13},{"id":38,"text":"he could n't confirm that","depth":13},{"id":39,"text":"but Rosenstein `` was definitely very concerned about the President , about his capacity and about his intent at that point in time . '' Rosenstein 's discussion of the 25th Amendment was `` just another kinda topic","depth":13},{"id":40,"text":"that he jumped to in the midst ... of a wide-ranging conversation , ''","depth":13},{"id":41,"text":"McCabe added .","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"Earlier Friday , a spokeswoman for McCabe disputed characterizations of the incident .","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"`` To clarify ,","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"at no time did Mr. McCabe participate in any extended discussions about the use of the 25th Amendment ,","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"nor is he aware of such discussions , ''","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"Melissa Schwartz said in a statement .","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"She said","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"McCabe was `` present and participated in a discussion","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"that included a comment by Deputy Attorney General","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"( Rod )","depth":12},{"id":51,"text":"Rosenstein","depth":12},{"id":52,"text":"regarding the 25th Amendment . ''","depth":12},{"id":53,"text":"In September ,","depth":13},{"id":54,"text":"citing sources familiar with memos","depth":14},{"id":55,"text":"authored by McCabe ,","depth":14},{"id":56,"text":"CNN reported","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"that Rosenstein discussed wearing a `` wire ''","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"to record conversations with Trump","depth":13},{"id":59,"text":"and recruiting Cabinet members","depth":14},{"id":60,"text":"to invoke the 25th Amendment","depth":15},{"id":61,"text":"to remove Trump from office .","depth":15},{"id":62,"text":"Also in September , an anonymous `` senior official in the Trump administration '' claimed in a New York Times op-ed","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"that there had been `` early whispers within the cabinet","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"of invoking the 25th Amendment . ''","depth":12},{"id":65,"text":"It was not mentioned in the material","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"released from the McCabe interview","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"if he or anyone else approached Cabinet members directly","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"to discuss the idea .","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"In a statement on Thursday , a Justice Department spokesperson said","depth":6},{"id":70,"text":"Rosenstein","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"-- who repeatedly disputed the `` wire '' revelation back in September --","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"again denied pursuing or advocating for the use of the 25th Amendment","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"to remove Trump from office .","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"`` As the Deputy Attorney General previously has stated ,","depth":7},{"id":75,"text":"based on his personal dealings with the President ,","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"there is no basis","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"to invoke the 25th Amendment ,","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"nor was the DAG in a position","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"to consider invoking the 25th Amendment , ''","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"the statement read .","depth":6},{"id":81,"text":"Both Trump and the White House on Thursday called McCabe a `` disgrace , ''","depth":6},{"id":82,"text":"with the White House saying","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"he had `` no credibility ''","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"and Trump accusing him of being politically biased during his time at the FBI .","depth":7},{"id":85,"text":"Vice President Mike Pence told MSNBC 's Andrea Mitchell on Thursday","depth":7},{"id":86,"text":"he has `` never heard any discussion of the 25th Amendment by members of this government","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"and I would never expect to . ''","depth":8},{"id":88,"text":"Senate Judiciary Chairman Lindsey Graham called McCabe 's comments `` a stunning revelation ''","depth":7},{"id":89,"text":"and that he would subpoena the former official to testify on Capitol Hill about the matter `` if I have to . ''","depth":7},{"id":90,"text":"In December , CNN reported","depth":7},{"id":91,"text":"that","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"following the firing of Comey ,","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"McCabe took the extraordinary step","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"of opening an obstruction of justice investigation into Trump","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"before special counsel Robert Mueller was appointed in May 2017 .","depth":9},{"id":96,"text":"In the interview","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"that aired Thursday ,","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"McCabe told Pelley","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"he `` wanted to make sure","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"that our case was on solid ground","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"and","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"if somebody came in behind me","depth":13},{"id":103,"text":"and closed it","depth":14},{"id":104,"text":"and tried to walk away from it ,","depth":14},{"id":105,"text":"they would not be able to do that","depth":12},{"id":106,"text":"without creating a record","depth":12},{"id":107,"text":"of why they made that decision . ''","depth":12},{"id":108,"text":"McCabe said","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"that the day after Comey 's firing and after meeting with Trump in the Oval Office ,","depth":10},{"id":110,"text":"`` I met with the team","depth":12},{"id":111,"text":"investigating the Russia cases","depth":12},{"id":112,"text":"and I asked the team to go back and conduct an assessment","depth":12},{"id":113,"text":"to determine where are we with these efforts","depth":13},{"id":114,"text":"and what steps do we need to take going forward . ''","depth":13},{"id":115,"text":"`` I was very concerned","depth":10},{"id":116,"text":"that I was able to put the Russia case on absolutely solid ground in an indelible fashion","depth":11},{"id":117,"text":"that ,","depth":12},{"id":118,"text":"were I removed quickly or reassigned or fired ,","depth":13},{"id":119,"text":"that the case could not be closed or vanish in the night","depth":14},{"id":120,"text":"without a trace , ''","depth":14},{"id":121,"text":"said McCabe ,","depth":10},{"id":122,"text":"who is promoting his forthcoming book , `` The Threat :","depth":11},{"id":123,"text":"How the FBI Protects America in the Age of Terror and Trump . ''","depth":11},{"id":124,"text":"In its statement on Thursday , the White House called McCabe 's investigation `` completely baseless . ''","depth":5},{"id":125,"text":"McCabe was fired by then-Attorney General Jeff Sessions in March","depth":4},{"id":126,"text":"following an inspector general report","depth":7},{"id":127,"text":"that concluded","depth":8},{"id":128,"text":"he misled investigators about his role","depth":9},{"id":129,"text":"in directing other officials at the FBI to speak to The Wall Street Journal about his involvement in a public corruption investigation into the Clinton Foundation .","depth":9},{"id":130,"text":"The Justice Department 's watchdog has referred his findings on McCabe to the US Attorney 's office in Washington for possible criminal charges .","depth":6},{"id":131,"text":"The case remains under investigation .","depth":5},{"id":132,"text":"CLARIFICATION :","depth":4},{"id":133,"text":"This story has been updated","depth":5},{"id":134,"text":"to more accurately characterize a statement from a Justice Department spokesperson .","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":269,"left":0,"right":268,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":268,"left":258,"right":267,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":258,"left":214,"right":257,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":214,"left":202,"right":213,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":202,"left":176,"right":201,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":176,"left":145,"right":175,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":145,"left":142,"right":144,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":142,"left":1,"right":141,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":141,"left":138,"right":140,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":138,"left":2,"right":137,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":137,"left":3,"right":136,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":136,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":140,"left":139,"right":8,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":139,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":144,"left":9,"right":143,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":143,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":175,"left":174,"right":42,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":174,"left":156,"right":173,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":156,"left":152,"right":155,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":152,"left":147,"right":151,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":147,"left":146,"right":14,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":146,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":151,"left":15,"right":150,"relation":"elaboration","nucle